    <item>
      <title>关税提高了消费者的价格，但退款只流向企业</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/companies-consumers-tariff-refunds.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多家庭都感受到了总统现在非法关税的刺痛，但企业几乎没有透露是否会分享返还给他们的 1,660 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/companies-consumers-tariff-refunds.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 13:57:43 GMT</pubDate>
