    <item>
      <title>谁可以获得关税退款？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/video/business/100000010852324/whos-getting-a-tariff-refund.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最高法院裁决推翻特朗普政府的多项关税后，进口商已开始申请 1,660 亿美元的退款。正如我们的经济政策记者托尼·罗姆（Tony Romm）所解释的那样，消费者不太可能看到大部分钱回到自己的口袋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/video/business/100000010852324/whos-getting-a-tariff-refund.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 10:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
